@WHO @WHOEMRO @WHO_Europe @WHOWPRO @WHOSEARO @WHOAFRO @pahowho It is simple to gently wipe your bills with dish soap/water in 🇨🇦 
Coins can be submerged in a diluted bowl of water & 2 sprays of Clorox disinfectant. Let sit for 2 mins and rinse in closed sink. After dry place in wallet. Keep dirty coins in separate ziplock bag. Be well 😊✌🏼 https://t.co/7Ca8MG538t
